      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:7:4:5:10",
      "relations": null,
      "text": [
        " كَانَ عَلِيٌّ ( عليه السلام ) يَقُولُ تُسْتَأْدَى دِيَةُ الْخَطَإِ فِي ثَلَاثِ سِنِينَ وَ تُسْتَأْدَى دِيَةُ الْعَمْدِ فِي سَنَةٍ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Muhammad Bin Yahya from Ahmad Bin Muhammad, and Ali Bin Ibrahim from his father, both together from Ibn Mahboub, from Abu Wallad, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘Ali<sup>asws</sup> was saying: ‘You have to pay the wergild of the erroneous (killing) within three years, and you have to pay the wergild of the deliberate (killing) within one year’."
        ]
      }
